{"tid":1113620,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE英文oral討論","createTime":"2019-04-18T04:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T04:41:20.000Z","uid":73910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4efbf0ba5f29ef58934216f848fbecde3e9040ed","tid":1113620,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:31:42.000Z","msg":"大家好，我4月尾就考DSE英文口試，<br />\n我有睇過pastpaper，大約知道分part A group interaction同part B individual，同埋份卷會比篇文章你睇<br />\n<br />\n但我唔係呢個年代既學生，所以其實唔太清楚個玩法，有d問題想問問大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）part A小組討論，係咪一定要用佢篇文章既內容去傾？考生可唔可以無視篇文，淨係講自己既point?<br />\n<br />\n2) 如果一定要用佢篇文既內容，咁我可唔可以再加d自己既point去討論？<br />\n<br />\n3）佢份卷會有幾題問題guide住考生，係咪一定要傾晒果幾條問題？我可唔可以自己開條新問題？<br />\n<br />\n4）考part B時，係咪一定要用篇文既內容去講？<br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485d55c1d6ab72967750960cf3b644efc1f1c7e3","tid":1113620,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:33:35.000Z","msg":"第3題問得唔太好，<br />\n我既意思係份卷會建議考生係part A傾既方向，想問係咪一定要討論晒佢建議既咁多題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cb4c4de67a6ecc25454bb47ce93c120ebf580b","tid":1113620,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:37:13.000Z","msg":"可以<br />\n可以<br />\n係<br />\n唔係"},{"pid":"397d256aaaed5ed04904d7eadae964bdac237464","tid":1113620,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93cb4c4de67a6ecc25454bb47ce93c120ebf580b","tid":1113620,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:37:13.000Z","msg":"可以<br />\n可以<br />\n係<br />\n唔係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"謝謝毛主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}